### AI SDK Demo API - HTTP Requests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-api-key-here

### Get API Information
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/info

### ============================================
### Forecasting Endpoints
### ============================================

### Forecast using Trend Analysis
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/forecast/trend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "historicalData": [
    { "date": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z", "value": 100 },
    { "date": "2024-02-01T00:00:00Z", "value": 120 },
    { "date": "2024-03-01T00:00:00Z", "value": 140 },
    { "date": "2024-04-01T00:00:00Z", "value": 160 },
    { "date": "2024-05-01T00:00:00Z", "value": 180 }
  ],
  "targetDate": "2024-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "confidenceLevel": 80
}

