### ============================================
### LLM Endpoints
### ============================================

### Generate LLM Completion
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/completion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Explain what artificial intelligence is in simple terms.",
  "provider": "OpenAI",
  "model": "gpt-4",
  "maxTokens": 500,
  "temperature": 0.7
}

### Generate LLM Chat Completion
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "What are the key differences between machine learning and deep learning?",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a helpful AI assistant specializing in technology."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I want to understand AI better."
    }
  ],
  "provider": "OpenAI",
  "model": "gpt-4"
}

