### Analyze Skills Gap (Rule-based)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/skills/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requiredSkills": [
    "C#",
    "ASP.NET Core",
    "Entity Framework",
    "Docker",
    "Kubernetes",
    "Microservices Architecture"
  ],
  "currentSkills": [
    "C#",
    "ASP.NET Core",
    "Entity Framework",
    "SQL Server"
  ],
  "useLLMForAnalysis": false
}

